title: Keplin - U-Shaped Metal Garden Pegs - 15cm Heavy-Duty Stakes - Galvanized Rust-Resistant Pins - Sharp Beveled Ends for Easy Ground Insertion -Secure Landscape (100 Pack)
features: DURABLE & HEAVY-DUTY SET – Includes 100 metal U-shaped pegs, offering strong and reliable ground anchoring for landscape fabric, weed membranes, artificial grass, and netting.

GALVANIZED & RUST-RESISTANT – These 15cm heavy-duty garden pegs are galvanized for extra protection, preventing rust and ensuring long-lasting performance for landscaping, ground sheets, and outdoor use.

SHARP BEVELED ENDS & WASHERS – The beveled peg ends allow for effortless ground penetration, while the washers provide extra grip, securing items tightly in place for gardening, tent setups, and tarpaulins.

MULTI-PURPOSE GARDEN STAPLES – Ideal for securing weed control fabric, ground covers, artificial turf, camping tarpaulins, and plant protection. The U-pins and washers ensure a secure and stable hold.

EASY TO USE WITH PICK HOOK – The set includes a sturdy pick hook for effortless peg removal and repositioning, making it ideal for reusable landscaping, gardening, and securing tents in windy conditions.
description: Product Description Galvanised and Zinc coated for rust prevention and to increase durability, Shaped with a wide head for easy installation, tips are sharp so its easier to dig into tough soil Staples are rust proof and are hard to bend, making them more durable, Ideal for securing ground sheets, netting, garden pipes, weed fabric, landscape fabric, bark coverings, hoses, cables, artificial grass, polythene sheets.
